%20be%20present%20in%20an%20AMUL%20ice%20cream%20tub%20packed%20at%20the%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20noted%20that%20a%20representative%20met%20the%20defendants%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20subject%20Amul%20ice%20cream%20tub%20so%20that%20it%20could%20be%20tested%20to%20verify%20their%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20stated%20that%20the%20plaintiff%20was%20willing%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter%20to%20ascertain%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20claims%20of%20defendants%201%20and%202.%20However%2C%20they%20refused%20to%20make%20available%20the%20said%20ice%20cream%20tub%20to%20the%20officials%20of%20the%20plaintiff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defendants%20no.%201%20and%202%20did%20not%20appear%20before%20the%20court%20despite%20the%20issuance%20of%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20record%20that%20defendants%20were%20served%20with%20an%20advance%20copy%20of%20the%20suit%20record%20in%20June%202024%20by%20the%20counsel%20for%20the%20plaintiff%20prior%20to%20its%20first%20listing%20on%20June%2028%3B%20however%2C%20none%20appeared%20for%20them%20either%20on%20June%2028%20or%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20has%20been%20listed%20for%20hearing%20on%20July%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720230480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-12%2Fcourt-generic-650x400_650x400_81450530482.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-court-directs-removal-of-post-alleging-centipede-in-amul-ice-cream-6044301%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20a%20social%20media%20user%2C%20a%20woman%2C%20to%20take%20down%20a%20post%20from%20X%20alleging%20a%20centipede%20in%20Amul%20ice%20cream.%20It%20al