%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F02%2Fpolitics%2Fjohn-kelly-donald-trump-us-service-members-veterans%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereportedly%20deriding%20veterans%20in%20private%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20Republicans%20hitting%20Biden%20for%20falsely%20claiming%20at%20last%20week's%20presidential%20debate%20that%20no%20US%20troops%20have%20died%20on%20his%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20both%20also%20have%20legislative%20track%20records%20from%20their%20first%20terms%20in%20office%2C%20as%20well%20as%20well-documented%20accounts%20of%20how%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.military.com%2Fbenefits%2Fveteran-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDepartment%20of%20Veterans%20Affairs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20functioned%20under%20their%20administrations%2C%20that%20could%20point%20to%20how%20a%20second%20term%20would%20play%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20shepherded%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.military.com%2Fbenefits%2Fveterans-health-care%2Fnew-law-expands-veterans-health-benefits.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPACT%20Act%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20been%20described%20as%20the%20biggest%20expansion%20of%20veterans%20benefits%20in%20a%20generation.%20Trump's%20biggest%20veterans-related%20legislation%20was%20the%20Mission%20Act%2C%20which%20expanded%20veterans'%20ability%20to%20seek%20VA-funded%20care%20outside%20of%20the%20VA%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20who%20may%20have%20benefited%20from%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Mission%20Act%2C%20for%20that%20individual%2C%20it's%20the%20most%20important%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patrick%20Murray%2C%20legislative%20director%20at%20the%20Veterans%20for%20Foreign%20Wars.%20%26quot%3BSomeone%20who%20may%20have%20had%20a%20rare%20cancer%20that%20was%20benefited%20by%20the%20PACT%20Act%2C%20that's%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20them.%20So%2C%20different%20veterans%20who%20had%20different%20illnesses%2C%20injuries%2C%20disabilities%2C%20whatever%2C%20may%20have%20benefited%20from%20either%20of%20the%20bills%20and%2C%20to%20those%20veterans%2C%20that's%20the%20most%20important%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20veterans%20groups%20echoed%20the%20importance%20of%20both%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20fought%20hard%20for%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Mission%20and%20PACT%20acts%20because%20all%20veterans%20deserve%20the%20best%20care%20possible%20from%20VA%2C%26quot%3B%20Chanin%20Nuntavong%2C%20the%20American%20Legion's%20executive%20director%20for%20government%20affairs%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FMilitary.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMilitary.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20untangling%20the%20knots%20often%20associated%20with%20securing%20their%20earned%20healthcare%20benefits%3B%20expanding%20the%20rules%20to%20cover%20all%20those%20eligible%3B%20and%20lifting%20barriers%20to%20access%2C%20especially%20to%20those%20who%20live%20in%20rural%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Joe%20Biden%20delivers%20a%20speech%20about%20the%20PACT%20Act%20while%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20poster%20that%20reads%20%26quot%3BSupport%20our%20Veterans%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668862e11f0c1cd6d731f6fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20delivers%20a%20speech%20about%20the%20PACT%20Act%20at%20the%20Westwood%20Park%20YMCA%20in%20Nashua%2C%20New%20Hampshire.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Tully%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PACT%20Act%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20yearslong%20effort%20from%20veterans%2C%20family%20members%2C%20and%20other%20advocates%20to%20get%20better%20recognition%20and%20care%20for%20ailments%20believed%20to%20be%20caused%20by%20exposure%20to%20burn%20pits%