y%20service%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Joe%20Parsetich%2C%20then%20the%20national%20commander%20for%20the%20Disabled%20American%20Veterans%2C%20said%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20passage%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mission%20Act%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20an%20effort%20to%20fix%20issues%20with%20the%20earlier%20Choice%20Act%2C%20a%202014%20law%20that%20was%20borne%20out%20of%20the%20VA%20wait-time%20scandal.%20Trump%20often%20incorrectly%20refers%20to%20his%20achievement%20as%20%26quot%3BChoice%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20the%20earlier%20bill%20with%20the%20same%20name%20was%20signed%20by%20his%20predecessor%2C%20President%20Barack%20Obama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Then-US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20holds%20up%20the%20VA%20Mission%20Act%20he%20signed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668862371aace5b3ada4d4bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThen-US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20holds%20up%20the%20VA%20Mission%20Act%20of%202018%20he%20signed%20at%20a%20ceremony%20in%20the%20Rose%20Garden%20of%20the%20White%20House.%3Cp%3ECheriss%20May%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mission%20Act%20expanded%20the%20number%20of%20veterans%20eligible%20to%20receive%20private%20healthcare%20funded%20by%20the%20VA%20and%20consolidated%20several%20different%20programs%20for%20community%20care%20into%20one.%20Under%20the%20law%2C%20veterans%20can%20seek%20outside%20care%20if%20they%20face%20more%20than%20a%2030-minute%20drive%20for%20primary%20care%20or%20mental%20health%20services%20or%2060%20minutes%20for%20specialty%20care%2C%20or%20a%2020-day%20wait%20for%20a%20primary%20care%20or%20mental%20health%20appointment%20and%20more%20than%2028%20days%20for%20specialty%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20VA%20under%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20undermined%20the