-charge-customers-d86ca9e4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20report%20from%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELake%20said%20the%20changes%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bbroad%2C%20sweeping%2C%20and%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20costs%20would%20be%20tacked%20onto%20services%20that%20have%20been%20free%20so%20far%2C%20like%20checking%20accounts%20and%20financial%20planning%20tools%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reviewed%20a%20Chase%20presentation%20that%20covered%20the%20expected%20impact%20of%20proposed%20regulations.%20The%20presentation%20estimated%20that%20two%20out%20of%20three%20consumers%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20fee%20for%20checking%20accounts%20if%20the%20cap%20went%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELake%20also%20said%20those%20impacted%20will%20be%20the%20ones%20%26quot%3Bwho%20can%20least%20afford%20to%20be%26quot%3B%20and%20credit%20access%20will%20also%20be%20more%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20regulations%20include%20a%20proposed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flower-credit-card-late-fees-limits-savings-us-economy-impact-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%248%20cap%20on%20late%20credit%20card%20payment%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20%243%20cap%20for%20overdrafting%20bank%20accounts.%20The%20limit%20is%20part%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20crackdown%20on%20hidden%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-banks-profit-overdraft-fees-surprise-biden-administration-wants-curb-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20estimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20about%2045%20million%20people%20are%20charged%20credit%20card%20late%20fees%20annually%2C%20and%20the%20change%20could%20save%20those%20people%20up%20to%20%24220%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20changes%20include%20limiting%20debit-card%20fees%20and%20how%20much%20banks%20can%20charge%20apps%20like%20Venmo%20and%20CashApp%20for%20accessing%20customer%20data%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20regulations%20would%20also%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20banks%20to%20lend%20money%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-lending-basel-distress-refinancing-bank-regulation-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erequiring%20banks%20to%20set%20aside%20more%20money%20as%20reserves%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20could%20make%20it%20more%20complicated%20for%20borrowers%20to%20qualify%20for%20loans%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChase%20is%20the%20biggest%20bank%20in%20the%20US%20and%20it's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20issuers%20of%20credit%20cards%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20other%20banks%20are%20expected%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20path%20%E2%80%94%20and%20several%20have%20already%20issues%20warnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Merchants%20Payments%20Coalition%2C%20Mastercard%20announced%20in%20April%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.bloomberglaw.com%2Fdaily-labor-report%2Fmastercard-still-raising-some-fees-on-retailers-after-settlement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eplanning%20to%20increase%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20certain%20credit-card%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiti's%20chief%20financial%20officer%2C%20Mark%20Mason%2C%20said%20in%20a%20January%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20bank%20planned%20to%20make%20up%20lost%20revenue%20with%20%26quot%3Boffsets%20and%20mitigants%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20didn't%20specify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapital%20One%20CEO%20Rich%20Fairbank%20also%20said%20in%20January%20that%20the%20new%20regulation%20would%20impact%20its%20profits%20and%20it%20would%20implement%20%26quot%3Bmitigating%20actions%26quot%3B%20to%20counteract%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-card-late-fees-cap-swipe-mastercard-visa-jpmorgan-rewards-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnalysts%20at%20UBS%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20investors%20in%20April%20that%20capping%20credit-card%20late%20fees%20and%20swipe%20fees%20in%20addition%20to%20lowering%20debit-card%20swipe%20fees%2C%20would%20push%20companies%20like%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20and%20American%20Express%20looking%20to%20make%20up%20the%20revenue%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20banks%20have%20threatened%20to%20take%20out%20the%20cost%20of%20new%20regulations%20on%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20financial%20crisis%20in%202008%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-banks-threaten-debit-card-cap-2011-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanks%20threatened%20to%20put%20caps%20on%20card%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20Congress%20approved%20rules%20limiting%20swipe%20fees.%20However%2C%20the%20threats%20were%20a%20bluff%3B%20few%20institutions%20followed%20through%20after%20customers%20themselves%20said%20they'd%20just%20switch%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20with%20Biden's%20crackdown%20on%20credit%20card%20companies%2C%20banks%20may%20keep%20to%20their%20word%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20the%20banks%20all%20decide%20to%20add%20new%20costs%20for%20consumers%2C%20giving%20them%20no%20place%20to%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchase-warns-pay-free-services-checking-account-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720208492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668827d91f0c1cd6d731e332%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchase-warns-pay-free-services-checking-account-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chase%20Bank%20boss%20Marianne%20Lake%20warns%20that%20the%20pain%20of%20making%20up%20lost%20profits%20may%20be%20passed%20on%20to%20consumer