erent-says-rahul-gandhi-on-agniveer-row-6043058%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%20Officials%20Of%20Secretary%20Rank%20Now%20Eligible%20To%20Be%20Telecom%20Regulator%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20notified%20rules%20under%20the%20Telecommunication%20Act%20which%20makes%20only%20secretary%20to%20the%20government%20or%20officials%20with%20equivalent%20rank%20eligible%20for%20the%20position%20of%20sector%20regulator%20Trai%20chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20made%20certain%20sections%20of%20the%20Act%20operational%20from%20June%2026%20and%20some%20of%20the%20rules%20of%20those%20sections%20have%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20July%205%2C%20including%20the%20criteria%20for%20appointment%20as%20Chairperson%20and%20Members%20of%20the%20Telecom%20Regulatory%20Authority%20of%20India%20(Trai)%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official%20statement%20issued%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCriteria%20for%20appointment%20as%20Chairperson%20and%20Members%20of%20TRAI%3A%20Section%2059(b)%20of%20the%20Act%20will%20amend%20section%204%20of%20the%20TRAI%20Act%201997%20and%20prescribes%20criteria%20for%20appointment%20of%20Chairperson%20and%20Members%20of%20TRAI%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20section%20restricts%20sector%20experts%20with%20professional%20experience%20in%20the%20field%20of%20telecommunication%2C%20industry%2C%20finance%2C%20accountancy%2C%20law%20etc.%20from%20becoming%20Trai%20chairperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProvided%20that%20a%20person%20who%20is%2C%20or%20has%20been%2C%20in%20the%20service%20of%20Government%20shall%20not%20be%20appointed...as%20a%20Chairperson%20unless%20such%20person%20has%20held%20the%20post%20of%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20or%20any%20equivalent%20post%20in%20the%20central%20government%20or%20the%20state%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20new%20Act%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20effective%20from%20July%205%20also%20include%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20unauthorised%20use%20of%20equipment%20which%20block%20telecommunications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Acts%20prescribes%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20the%20use%20of%20any%20equipment%20which%20blocks%20telecommunication%2C%20unless%20permitted%20by%20the%20central%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20for%20optimal%20utilisation%20of%20spectrum%20has%20also%20become%20effective%20from%20July%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Act%20provides%20a%20legal%20framework%20for%20efficient%20utilization%20of%20scarce%20spectrum%20through%20processes%20such%20as%20secondary%20assignment%2C%20sharing%2C%20trading%2C%20leasing%20and%20surrender%20of%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20enables%20the%20utilisation%20of%20spectrum%20in%20a%20flexible%2C%20liberalised%20and%20technologically%20neutral%20manner.%20It%20also%20empowers%20the%20central%20government%20to%20establish%20an%20enforcement%20and%20monitoring%20mechanism%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20PTI%20PRS%20HVA%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720200060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftb5h2h2k_telecom-generic-telecom-aution-generic-ians_625x300_26_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovt-notifies-rules-under-telecom-act-to-make-only-govt-secretary-level-official-eligible-for-trai-chiefs-post-6042537%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20notified%20rules%20under%20the%20Telecommunication%20Act%20which%20makes%20only%20secretary%20to%20the%20government%20or%20officials%20with%20equivalent%20rank%20eligible%20for%20the%20position%20of%20sector%20regulator%20Trai%20chairman.%22%2C%22auth