ps%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fafdq2shg_adani-generic_625x300_03_February_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jethmalani%20referred%20to%20Anla%20Cheng%2C%20a%20businesswoman%20who%20is%20under%20investigation%20in%20the%20US%20for%20allegedly%20subverting%20US%20interests%20and%20promoting%20China's%20strategic%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%20I%20didn't%20know%20about%20Anla%20Cheng.%20China%20is%20extremely%20upset%20about%20having%20lost%20three%20bits%2C%20to%20my%20knowledge%2C%20of%20overseas%20projects%20of%20strategic%20interests%20-%20a%20railway%20line%20in%20Australia%3B%20a%20port%20in%20Jaffna%2C%20and%20a%20port%20in%20Haifa%2C%20Israel.%20That%20was%20the%20most%20important%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20hit%20job%20was%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20losing%20of%20these%20contracts.%20Why%20the%20Congress%20party%20has%20gotten%20into%20it%20with%20such%20gusto%2C%20only%20they%20can%20explain%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20lawyer%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20new%20facts%20have%20come%20to%20light%20after%20Hindenburg's%20response%20to%20a%20notice%20by%20the%20capital%20markets%20regulator%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20became%20public.%20Hindenburg%20has%20said%20it%20was%20only%20a%20researcher%20that%20was%20given%20a%20contract%20by%20a%20company%20owned%20by%20US-based%20fund%20manager%20Mark%20E%20Kingdon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20trust%20fund%20in%20which%20Mr%20Kingdon%20and%20his%20Chinese-origin%20wife%2C%20Anla%20Cheng%2C%20held%2036%20per%20cent%20was%20used%20in%20the%20hit%20job%20against%20Adani%20Group%20companies%2C%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%20they%20also%20entered%20into%20an%20agreement%20with%20a%20Kotak%20investment%20outfit%2C%20which%20set%20up%20a%20special%20purpose%20vehicle%20KIOS%20(Kotak%20India%20Opportunity%20Fund).%20This%20was%20meant%20for%20starting%20a%20trading%20account%20for%20the%20couple's%20company...%20They%20did%20not%20wait%20for%20the%20%5BHindenburg%5D%20report%20to%20come%20out%20before%20they%20took%20certain%20steps.%20So%20the%20trading%20account%20was%20started%3B%20money%20%5Bfrom%20the%20family%20fund%5D%20was%20given%20by%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrima%20facie%2C%20a%20bulk%20of%20the%20money%20earned%20out%20of%20this%20-%20%2425%20million%20-%20went%20to%20the%20Kingdons.%20That%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20the%20entire%20figure.%20More%20study%20is%20needed.%20SEBI%20may%20need%20to%20put%20more%20questions%20to%20Hindenburg.%20We%20don't%20know%20the%20entire%20size%20of%20the%20cake%2C%20but%20a%20portion%20of%20it%20was%20to%20go%20to%20Hindenburg.%20So%2C%20Hindenburg%20was%20the%20researcher%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20trading%20op%20was%20the%20couple's%20fund%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fvphsefag_kotak-mahindra-bank_625x300_02_July_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Kotak's%20role%2C%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20said%20the%20Indian%20bank%20certainly%20knew%20this%20was%20a%20short%20sell%2C%20bear-hammering%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20report%20was%20even%20made%20public%2C%20they%20had%20already%20taken%20short%20positions%20in%20Adani%20shares.%20Kotak%20certainly%20knew%20this%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20short%20sell%20trade%20in%20Adani%20shares.%20They%20covered%20the%20short%20sell%20after%20putting%20the%20margin%20money%20up%2C%20after%20the%20report%20was%20issued%20and%20shares%20fell.%20So%20that's%20how%20short%20sellers%2C%20bear-hammers%20make%20their%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindenburg%20seems%20to%20be%20taking%20an%20arm's%20length%20position%20on%20the%20couple%20and%20their%20fund.%20Whoever%20among%20them%20approached%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Investments%20Limited%20%5BKIOS%20was%20the%20special%20purpose%20vehicle%5D%2C%20what%20we%20do%20know%20is%20that%20Kotak%20was%20the%20one%20who%20knew%20who%20were%20involved.%20Hindenburg%20seems%20to%20have%20said%20'we're%20only%20the%20researcher%20for%20%5Bstudying%5D%20Adani%20companies%20and%20we%20were%20supposed%20to%20get%20a%20cut'.%20So%20they%20also%20knew%20it%20was%20a%20short%20sell%20operation.%20But%20only%20Kotak%20knew%20who%20the%20investors%20were%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Chinese-American%20businesswoman%20Anla%20Cheng%20is%20an%20extremely%20controversial%20person%20even%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20She%20ran%20SupChina%20%5Blater%20renamed%20to%20The%20China%20Project%5D%2C%20which%20was%20pro-China%20and%20promoted%20Chinese%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20insider%20-%20this%20is%20where%20one%20got%20all%20the%20information%20from%20-%20Shannon%20Van%20Sant%2C%20ex%20employee%20of%20Cheng's%20company%2C%20in%20her%20sworn%20statement%20said%20Cheng%20was%20subverting%20US%20interests%20and%20promoting%20China's%20strategic%20interests.%20She%20found%20the%20entire%20operation%20to%20be%20extremely%20fishy%2C%20a%20hub%20of%20Chinese%20spies%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jethmalani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20US%20Congress%20took%20up%20the%20matter%2C%20SupChina%20morphed%20into%20another%20company%20called%20'The%20China%20Project'%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20because%20of%20the%20heat%20it%20faced%20from%20the%20US%20legislature%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20all%20its%20operations%2C%20The%20China%20Project%20announced%20publicly%20they%20are%20shutting%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720197300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07