%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkansas-top-court-rejects-2-anti-abortion-laws-bolstering-a-state-right-to-abortion-access%2Farticleshow%2F111519697.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkansas-top-court-rejects-2-anti-abortion-laws-bolstering-a-state-right-to-abortion-access%2Famp_articleshow%2F111519697.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkansas-top-court-rejects-2-anti-abortion-laws-bolstering-a-state-right-to-abortion-access%2Famp_articleshow%2F111519697.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHelp%20Accident%20Victims%26quot%3B%3A%20Lessons%20In%20Essay%20From%20Porsche%20Teen%20Who%20Killed%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20teenager%20who%20rammed%20his%20father's%20Porsche%20into%20two%20techies%20in%20Pune%20in%20May%2C%20killing%20them%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20was%20given%20bail%20and%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20road%20safety%20had%20sparked%20national%20outrage.%20NDTV%20has%20now%20accessed%20the%20essay%2C%20in%20which%20the%2017-year-old%20explains%20why%20he%20left%20the%20spot%20after%20the%20accident%20and%20stresses%20on%20the%20need%20to%20follow%20traffic%20rules.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeeting%20the%20bail%20conditions%20set%20by%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20on%20May%2019%2C%20the%20day%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20the%20teenager%20handed%20in%20the%20essay%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20builder%2C%20had%20been%20drinking%20with%20his%20friends%20in%20two%20pubs%20to%20celebrate%20his%20Class%2012%20results%20before%20knocking%20down%20the%20scooter%20carrying%20the%20two%2024-year-old%20techies%20-%20Ashwini%20Koshta%20and%20Anish%20Awadhiya%20-%20in%20the%20Porsche%20at%20a%20speed%20in%20excess%20of%20150%20kmph.%20He%20had%20then%20sped%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20essay%2C%20the%2017-year-old%2C%20who%20was%20four%20months%20shy%20of%20the%20legal%20age%20for%20driving%20and%20more%20than%20seven%20years%20shy%20of%20Maharashtra's%20legal%20age%20for%20drinking%2C%20said%20he%20left%20the%20spot%20because%20he%20was%20scared%20of%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20him%20and%20of%20getting%20into%20trouble%20with%20the%20police.%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20also%20prevented%20him%20from%20going%20to%20a%20police%20station%20and%20reporting%20the%20accident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20that%2C%20instead%20of%20fleeing%20after%20an%20accident%2C%20people%20should%20go%20to%20the%20nearest%20police%20station%20and%20report%20what%20had%20happened.%20Not%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20said%2C%20could%20land%20people%20in%20trouble.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExhorting%20people%20to%20help%20accident%20victims%2C%20the%20teenager%20also%20said%20everyone%20should%20follow%20traffic%20rules%20for%20their%20own%20safety%20and%20that%20of%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Confident%20And%20Composed'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20essay%2C%20officials%20said%20they%20found%20it%20ambiguous%20and%20couldn't%20make%20out%20the%20teenager's%20mental%20state.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20while%20he%20was%20in%20the%20remand%20home%2C%20his%20behaviour%20was%20like%20someone%20who%20was%20older%20than%20he%20is%20and%20remained%20confident%20and%20composed%20even%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20his%20parents%20and%20grandfather.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20the%20teenager%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20Yerawada%20police%20station%2C%20where%20he%20was%20allegedly%20given%20VIP%20treatment%20and%20even%20given%20pizzas%20and%20burgers.%20Sunil%20Tingre%2C%20an%20MLA%20from%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20had%20also%20reached%20the%20police%20station%2C%20allegedly%20to%20ask%20police%20officials%20to%20go%20easy%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20murky%20saga%20began%20after%20that%2C%20with%20the%20boy's%20family%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20pin%20the%20crime%20on%20a%20driver%20and%20bribing%20doctors%20to%20get%20the%20teenager's%20blood%20samples%20exchanged%20before%20the%20blood%20alcohol%20test.%20The%20boy%20had%20got%20bail%20the%20same%20day%2C%20only%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20remand%20home%20following%20national%20outrage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20June%2C%20his%20detention%20was%20declared%20illegal%20by%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20ordered%20his%20immediate%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20High%20Court%20order%2C%20Ashwini%20Koshta's%20mother%20Mamta%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20shocked%20after%20seeing%20the%20news.%20I%20have%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20judiciary.%20They%20must%20have%20made%20the%20decision%20after%20careful%20consideration.%20However%2C%20I%20request%20the%20judges%20to%20understand%20the%20pain%20of%20a%20mother%20who%20has%20lost%20her%20daughter.%20Punishment%20should%20be%20given%20accordingly%20so%20that%20the%20public%20can%20trust%20the%20judicial%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720192080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Feoj00p2o_pune-porsche-_625x300_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-case-pune-porsche-accident-follow-traffic-rules-lessons-in-essay-from-teen-who-killed-2-in-porsche-6041886%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fact%20that%20the%20teenager%20who%20rammed%20his%20father's%20Porsche%20into%20two%20techies%20in%20Pune%20in%20May%2C%20killing%20them%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20was%20given%20bail%20and%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20road%20safety%20had%20sparked%20national%20outrage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-case-pune-porsche-accident-follow-tra