onstable-turned-self-styled%20godman%20Bhole%20Baba%20whose%20'satsang'%20(religious%20gathering)%20ended%20in%20a%20deadly%20stampede%20will%20show%20up%20%26quot%3Bvery%20soon%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20his%20lawyer%2C%20insisting%20that%20he%20would%20also%20assist%20the%20probe%20teams%20in%20their%20investigation.%20Bhole%20Baba%20aka%20Narayan%20Saakar%20Hari%20has%20not%20been%20seen%20in%20public%20since%20the%20crowd%20crush%20that%20killed%20121%20people%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Hathras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba's%20lawyer%20claimed%20that%20the%20trust%20would%20take%20care%20of%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20families%20of%20those%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20district-wise%20lists%20of%20the%20victims%20and%20Narayan%20Saakar%20Hari's%20trust%20would%20take%20care%20of%20the%20education%2C%20health%20and%20wedding%20expenses%20of%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20died%20in%20the%20stampede%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20lawyer%20AP%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stampede%20at%20the%20event%20that%20saw%202.5%20lakh%20devotees%20in%20attendance%20began%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20%26quot%3Bfollowers%20started%20to%20collect%20dust%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20ground%20where%20the%20preacher's%20car%20had%20passed.%20Men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20fell%20over%20each%20other%2C%20getting%20crushed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20huge%20turnout%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20there%20were%20too%20many%20people%20at%20the%20gathering%20because%20no%20'satsangs'%20were%20held%20from%20February%20to%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20had%20only%20given%20permission%20for%2080%2C000%20people%20to%20attend%20the%20sermon%2C%20less%20than%20a%20third%20of%20the%20number%20that%20turned%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20that%20his%20client%20was%20not%20to%20blame%20for%20the%20disaster%20and%20was%20not%20on%20the%20run.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20reason%20for%20him%20to%20hide.%20He%20has%20never%20hidden%20in%20his%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20believes%20in%20the%20law.%20He%20is%20following%20police%20directions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20people%20had%20been%20arrested%20so%20far%20for%20their%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20disaster%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20were%20members%20of%20the%20organising%20committee%20for%20the%20sermon.%20Baba%2C%20who%20cultivated%20a%20large%20following%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20has%20not%20been%20named%20in%20the%20First%20Information%20Report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20mainly%20working%20as%20volunteers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20engaged%20in%20crowd%20management%20and%20collecting%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20probing%20the%20Hathras%20stampede%20has%20recorded%20statements%20of%2090%20people%20so%20far%2C%20SIT%20chief%20Anupam%20Kulshrestha%20said%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BDefinitely%2C%20the%20gathered%20evidence%20suggests%20culpability%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20event%20organisers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20also%20gave%20an%20update%20on%20Devprakash%20Madhukar%2C%20a%20key%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20stampede.%20He%20is%20being%20treated%20in%20a%20hospital.%20As%20soon%20as%20he%20recovers%2C%20he%20will%20be%20produced%20before%20the%20SIT%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720191840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fd0fnf8ag_hathras-gathering-pti_625x300_05_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-bhole-babas-lawyer-explains-mad-rush-at-satsang-where-121-were-killed-6042071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20constable-turned-self-styled%20godman%20Bhole%20Baba%20whose%20'satsang'%20(religious%20gathering)%20ended%20in%20a%20deadly%