0Narendra%20Modi%20might%20collapse%20next%20month%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Central%20government%20is%20very%20weak%20and%20might%20collapse%20in%20August%20this%20year.%20It%20will%20allow%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20form%20a%20new%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Lalu%20Prasad%20said%2C%20addressing%20the%20RJD%20leaders%20and%20workers%20on%20the%2028th%20Foundation%20Day%20of%20RJD%20at%20the%20party's%20head%20office%20in%20Patna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERJD%20was%20founded%20on%20July%205%2C%201997%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav.%20The%20party%20had%20the%20backing%20of%20only%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20eight%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20at%20its%20inception.%20It%20had%20the%20support%20of%20many%20senior%20leaders%2C%20including%20Raghuvansh%20Prasad%20Singh%2C%20Mohammad%20Shahabuddin%2C%20Mohammad%20Taslimuddin%2C%20Ali%20Asraf%20Fatmi%2C%20and%20Abdul%20Bari%20Siddiqui.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20Assembly%20election%20could%20happen%20at%20any%20time%2C%20Lalu%20Yadav%20said%2C%20asking%20party%20workers%20to%20stay%20strong%2C%20implying%20that%20their%20strength%20would%20contribute%20to%20the%20party's%20overall%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20commended%20his%20son%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20for%20his%20hard%20work%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20party%20winning%20four%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20noted%20that%20Tejashwi%20Yadav's%20efforts%20in%20the%20last%20Assembly%20elections%20helped%20establish%20RJD%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20will%20make%20all%20the%20party's%20decisions%20for%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RJD%20Chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20Yadav%20criticised%20both%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20in%20his%20address%20to%20the%20workers%20and%20emphasised%20that%20despite%20being%20in%20power%20or%20Opposition%2C%20the%20party%20and%20its%20leadership%20never%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRJD%20turned%20into%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20in%202020.%20Although%2C%20they%20cheated%20and%20deliberately%20defeated%20us%20in%20that%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20RJD%20was%20able%20to%20get%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20done%20in%20Bihar%20only%20within%2017%20months%2C%20which%20was%20aimed%20at%20the%20advancement%20of%20the%20backward%20and%20extremely%20backward%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20is%20against%20reservation%20and%20constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said%20that%20the%20BJP's%20goal%20of%20winning%20over%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20fell%20significantly%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNarendra%20Modi%20is%20the%20weakest%20Prime%20Minister.%20He%20will%20not%20complete%20his%20five-year%20term.%20If%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20had%20won%2010%20more%20seats%2C%20Modi%20might%20not%20have%20become%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720190160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F4jmtsdl_lalu-prasad-yadav_625x300_30_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fweak-central-government-might-collapse-next-month-claims-lalu-yadav-6041386%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20'weak'%20central%20government%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20might%20collapse%20next%20month%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20cl