ming%20and%20felt%20a%20connection%20with%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20might%20find%20it%20odd%20that%20a%20youngster%20wanted%20to%20take%20up%20farming%20as%20a%20profession%2C%20it%20was%20all%20Lobo%20had%20ever%20wanted.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20wanted%20to%20try%20out%20new%20ways%20of%20growing%20plants%20effectively%20and%20profitably.%20I%20knew%20getting%20into%20the%20profession%20that%20it%20is%20more%20passion-driven%20than%20profit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20my%20family%20land%20was%20stuck%20in%20a%20conflict%20and%20I%20could%20not%20farm%20on%20it.%20We%20come%20from%20humble%20backgrounds%20and%20those%20lands%20were%20our%20only%20support.%20My%20dream%20seemed%20to%20be%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20a%20moment%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20keep%20going.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-1-1719992669.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lobo%20grows%20200%20varieties%20of%20plants%20on%20his%20terrace%20garden%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-1-1719992669.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-1-1719992669-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-1-1719992669-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-1-1719992669-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-1-1719992669-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355315%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELobo%20grows%20200%20varieties%20of%20plants%20on%20his%20terrace%20garden%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELobo%2C%20with%20his%20knowledge%20of%20farming%20and%20plants%2C%20started%20consulting%20and%20landscaping%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20farms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20my%20family%20eats%20well.%20The%20market%20is%20full%20of%20chemical-laden%20food%20and%20I%20could%20not%20allow%20myself%20to%20consume%20it.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20practise%20farming%20on%20my%20terrace.%20It%20was%20not%20very%20big%20but%20enough%20to%20follow%20my%20dream%20and%20make%20sure%20my%20family%20eats%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELobo%20started%20to%20look%20for%20online%20resources%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263989%2Findian-farmer-youtube-channel-influence-agriculture-tips-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20YouTube%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20set%20up%20a%20terrace%20garden.%20Currently%2C%20he%20grows%2032%20jasmine%20plants%20in%20his%20terrace%20garden%2C%20three%20of%20them%20using%20the%20hydroponics%20method%2C%20along%20with%20200%20varieties%20of%20fruits%20like%20mulberry%2C%20chikoo%2C%20and%20mangoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrowing%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20mango%20variety%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20been%20growing%20various%20varieties%20of%20gulf%20berries%20on%20my%20terrace%20and%20was%20also%20growing%20some%20mangoes%20as%20well.%20When%20I%20had%20successfully%20grown%20these%2C%20why%20not%20try%20Miyazaki%3F%20I%20knew%20that%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20grow%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20realising%20the%20monetary%20value%20of%20the%20variety%2C%20he%20treated%20it%20like%20any%20other%20mango%20plant.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20I%20did%20not%20give%20any%20special%20attention%20to%20the%20plant.%20I%20fed%20it%20my%20original%20and%20usual%20mixture%20that%20I%20give%20to%20all%20my%20other%20plants.%20It%20took%20the%20plant%20three-and-a-half%20years%20to%20yield.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20its%20value%20was%2C%20so%20my%20family%20and%20I%20consumed%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20news%20reporter%20who%20was%20doing%20a%20story%20on%20my%20terrace%20farm%20who%20recognised%20the%20mango%E2%80%99s%20worth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20after%20that%20report%20that%20I%20realised%20that%20it%20cost%20so%20much.%20Since%20then%2C%20I%20have%20been%20getting%20requests%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20grow%20it.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20much%20to%20share%20except%20my%20soil%20mix%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20variety%2C%20Lobo%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20variety%20comes%20from%20Japan%20which%20does%20not%20have%20the%20right%20weather%20conditions%20to%20grow%20mangoes%2C%20and%20the%20farmers%20usually%20use%20polyhouse%20techniques%20to%20grow%20them.%20The%20mango%20is%20known%20for%20its%20various%20health%20benefits%20and%20distinctive%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20%E2%80%98magic%E2%80%99%20mixture%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20make%20it%20at%20home%20and%20it%20contains%20nine%20minerals.%20It%20is%20made%20using%20cow%20dung%2C%20sheep%20manure%2C%20homemade%20curd%2C%20and%20vegetable%20waste.%20This%20mixture%20has%20a%20high%20nutritional%20value%20that%20helps%20the%20plant%20grow.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-2-1719992674.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lobo%20does%20not%20use%20any%20chemical%20p