0with%20a%20humorous%20means%20of%20%26quot%3Bwashing%20off%26quot%3B%20the%20mental%20and%20physical%20fatigue%20that%20comes%20with%20their%20jobs-often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bwork%20smell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20the%20smells%20of%20sweat%2C%20cigarette%20smoke%2C%20or%20coffee%20during%20commuting%20and%20office%20hours%2C%20the%20phrase%20captures%20the%20sense%20of%20exhaustion%20and%20stress%20that%20follows%20a%20demanding%20day.%20This%20trend%20shows%20how%20Chinese%20workers%20are%20increasingly%20turning%20to%20lighthearted%20internet%20activities%20as%20a%20way%20to%20decompress%20and%20escape%20from%20work-related%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3268638%2Fchina-youth-playfully-list-jobs-colleagues-sale-online-rid-work-pressures%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20search%20on%20Xianyu%20by%20the%20Post%20revealed%20more%20than%20500%20posts%20selling%20%26quot%3Bannoying%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20bosses%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhated%20colleagues%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20prices%20ranging%20from%202%20yuan%20(30%20US%20cents)%20to%2080%2C000%20yuan%20(US%2411%2C000).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20seller%20from%20central%20China%20listed%20her%20job%20for%208%2C000%20yuan%20(US%241%2C100).%20She%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BBecause%20I%20really%20don't%20want%20to%20wake%20up%20early%20anymore!%20This%20job%20pays%203%2C000%20yuan%20(US%24400)%20a%20month%2C%20so%20you%20can%20recoup%20your%20investment%20in%20three%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20seller%20from%20Beijing%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BSelling%20a%20colleague%20who%20is%20very%20good%20at%20being%20sarcastic%20for%203%2C999%20yuan%20(US%24550).%20I%20can%20teach%20you%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20this%20colleague%20and%20offer%2010%20tips%20to%20avoid%20being%20the%20scapegoat%20at%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomeone%20else%20listed%20his%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20boss%26quot%3B%20for%20500%20yuan%2C%20claiming%20that%20their%20personalities%20clashed%20and%20that%20the%20boss%20frequently%20criticised%20him%2C%20causing%20significant%20mental%20stress.%20Another%20seller%20from%20Beijing%20listed%20a%20project%20document%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20completed%20that%20night%20for%2010%20yuan%20(US%241.4)%2C%20reported%20the%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720185480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ftli5d6d_work-stress_625x300_05_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fselling-a-terrible-boss-lighthearted-trend-takes-over-chinese-social-media-6041414%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20humorous%20trend%20reflects%20the%20growing%20pressure%20faced%20by%20Chinese%20youth%20and%20their%20search%20for%20lighthearted%20outlets%20to%20cope%20with%20work-related%20exhaustion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fselling-a-terrible-boss-lighthearted-trend-takes-over-chinese-social-media-6041414%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fselling-a-terrible-boss-lighthearted-trend-takes-over-chinese-social-media-6041414%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fselling-a-terrible-boss-lighthearted-trend-takes-over-chinese-social-media-6041414%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I'm%20free%2C'%20says%20Andrew%20Tate%20as%20court%20rules%20he%20can%20leave%20Romania%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720185360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-andrew-tate_6547585.jpg%3F20240508170313%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fandrew-tate-says-he-can-leave-romania-while-awaiting-trial-13173605%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andrew%20Tate%20will%20be%20allowed%2