0It%20also%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpoultry%20waste%20needs%20urgent%20attention%20as%20a%20formal%20management%20does%20not%20exist%20for%20this%20waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20estimated%20that%20the%20generation%20of%20poultry%20waste%20is%20approximately%2020%20tonnes%20per%20day%2C%20just%20within%20the%20city%20of%20Ahmedabad.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bpoultry%20waste%5D%20is%20either%20sold%20to%20middlemen%20(for%20processing%20some%20body%20parts%20into%20fish%20feed%2C%20manure%20etc)%20or%20disposed%20of%20in%20municipal%20dumping%20sites%20without%20any%20treatment%2C%20which%20is%20against%20the%20law%20and%20is%20causing%20issues%20related%20to%20environmental%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Radhesh%20is%20able%20to%20make%20natural%20wool-like%20fibre%20similar%20to%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20wool%2C%20and%20silk.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERadhesh%20can%20make%20natural%20wool-like%20fibre%20similar%20to%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20wool%2C%